snippet.textDisplay:
Alhumdulilah! Thank you to all the wonderful and amazing fans who are going above and beyond to show love for Harkalay. Working on this song as co-writer and co-composer is such a beautiful honor especially because of the love you (the fans) breathe into it.

Big respect to the entire team it took to make this piece of art a reality. Everyone involved has so much passion, dedication and kindness for the project and it shows. All of you have already made our dreams to share music and connect with the world a reality and I pray it continues to inspire you all to work hard at yours.
It's all possible inshallah! Thank you all. ❤ Be the light in everyone's lives!
